        <section name="DataNucleus JPA API">
            <p>
                <i>datanucleus-api-jpa</i> provides support for the DataNucleus JPA implementation.
                <b>Note that in versions prior to 3.0 this was called <i>datanucleus-jpa</i></b>
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li>Compile Requirement : JDK1.5+</li>
                <li>Runtime Requirement : JDK1.5+</li>
                <li>Latest version : 3.3.4</li>
                <li>Roadmap : <a href="http://issues.datanucleus.org/browse/NUCJPA?report=com.atlassian.jira.plugin.system.project:roadmap-panel" target="_blank">Via JIRA</a></li>
                <li>License : <a href="../project/license.html">Apache 2</a></li>
                <li>Javadocs : <a href="../javadocs/api.jpa/3.3">3.3</a>,
                               <a href="../javadocs/api.jpa/3.2">3.2</a>,
                               <a href="../javadocs/api.jpa/3.1">3.1</a>,
                               <a href="../javadocs/api.jpa/3.0">3.0</a>,
                               <a href="../javadocs/jpa/2.1">2.1</a>,
                               <a href="../javadocs/jpa/2.0">2.0</a>,
                               <a href="../javadocs/jpa/1.1">1.1</a></li>
                <li>Source : <a href="https://sourceforge.net/p/datanucleus/code/HEAD/tree/platform/api.jpa/trunk/">latest</a></li>
            </ul>

            <subsection name="Source Code">
                <p>trunk can be checked out as follows</p>
<source>svn co https://svn.code.sf.net/p/datanucleus/code/platform/api.jpa/trunk api.jpa</source>
                <br/>
            </subsection>

            <subsection name="Download">
                <p><i>datanucleus-api-jpa</i> is downloadable as following</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><b>Releases</b> <a href="http://repo1.maven.org/maven2/org/datanucleus/datanucleus-api-jpa/" target="_blank">from Maven Central</a></li>
                    <li><b>Nightly builds</b> <a href="http://www.datanucleus.org/downloads/maven2-nightly/org/datanucleus/datanucleus-api-jpa/" target="_blank">from Maven2 Nightly Repository</a></li>
                </ul>
                <br/>
            </subsection>

